<h1>楚楚动人</h1>
<h2>（汉语词汇）</h2>
<a class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" href="javascript:;" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=81502" nslog-type="90000102" target="_blank"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num">999</span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">楚楚动人是一个汉语成语，读音为chǔ chǔ dòng rén，形容姿容美好，动人心神，楚楚：鲜明整洁的样子。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":1," data-sup="1">
[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_11094677"> </a>
指纤弱的样子，今多用以形容女子姿容神态柔弱动人。出自《诗经·曹风·蜉蝣》。</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div class="basic-info cmn-clearfix">
<dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-left">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">中文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
楚楚动人
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">拼    音</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
chǔ chǔ dòng rén
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">释    义</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
形容姿容美好，动人心神
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">近义词</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
<a href="/item/%E6%A5%9A%E6%A5%9A%E5%8F%AF%E4%BA%BA" target="_blank">楚楚可人</a>
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">反义词</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
<a href="/item/%E6%90%94%E9%A6%96%E5%BC%84%E5%A7%BF" target="_blank">搔首弄姿</a>
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">出    处</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
《<a href="/item/%E8%AF%97%E7%BB%8F" target="_blank">诗经</a>·曹风·蜉蝣》
</dd>
</dl></div>
